snippet.title: TD Worlds Release Trailer
snippet.description:
TD Worlds is a dynamic, highly strategical game that challenges your skill. Build an impenetrable defense and get ready to plunge into a new, unknown world to uncover its secrets.

Steam (demo available): https://store.steampowered.com/app/1659180/TD_Worlds/
Itch.io demo: https://newoldmax.itch.io/td-worlds-demo
Twitter: https://twitter.com/TDWorlds_game
Discord: https://discord.gg/tjkqhEsFGT

Music made by Nikita Voznesensky: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCFI11j5wB2AkX6VXOjfeIDg
